运动队在新单曲“Bang Bang Bang”中反思美国的枪支文化https://www.nme.com/news/music/sports-team-reflect-on-gun-culture-in-america-on-new-single-bang-bang-bang-3827985?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=运动队反思美国枪支文化新单曲棒棒棒Anagricel DuranFri, 10 Jan 2025 18:14:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3827985 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="运动队“Bang Bang Bang”可视化。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首单曲是乐队在美国巡演的第一晚在美国遭遇抢劫的一个月后发行的。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sports-team-reflect-on-gun-culture-in-america-on-new-single-bang-bang-bang-3827985">运动队在新单曲“Bang Bang Bang”中反思美国的枪支文化，</a>该单曲首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="运动队“Bang Bang Bang”可视化。图片来源：新闻界" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Sports-Team-Bang-Bang-Bang-visualiser.-Credit-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Sports-Team">Sports Team</a>发布了他们的新单曲“Bang Bang Bang”，反映了美国的枪支文化。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sports-team-interview-2022-gulp-album-3280946">运动队：“我们已经到了不可避免的地步”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 《Bang Bang Bang》由马泰斯·特莱兹（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/girl-in-red">《红衣女孩》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">《CMAT》</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯</a>）制作，以西方吉他连复段和嚎叫开场。与此同时，主唱亚历克斯·赖斯 (Alex Rice) 唱道： <em>“小吉米数学得了 B，头中两枪/华盛顿得到了晚餐约会和精美的 IPA/而牛顿仍然得到了机器人电话/来自全国步枪协会，</em> ”思考美国枪支文化局外人视角下的美国。</p><p>这首歌曲由 Sports Team 自己执导和制作，在视觉效果中可以看到一名穿着红色 T 恤和牛仔裤的男子跳舞的片段，与悬挂在白色工作室周围的剑桥六人组的片段混合在一起。</p><p>看看下面。 </p><p><iframe title="运动队 - Bang Bang Bang（歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1C-FaVziZEs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此后，这首歌对乐队来说有了更深层次和更黑暗的意义，因为最初是为了从局外人的角度看待美国的枪支文化，而在乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sports-team-robbed-at-gunpoint-in-california-ahead-of-their-us-tour-3818500">最近在美国第一次约会时就被持枪抢劫后，这首歌变得更贴近他们的内心。旅游。</a></p><p> Sports Team 在其 Instagram 帐户上分享了一段视频，视频中一群武装人员于 2024 年 12 月 3 日在一家咖啡店闯入了该团体的短跑货车。停下来喝咖啡。一名男子跑进来说有人撞上了一辆货​​车。跑出去试图阻止它，却发现蒙面人正在洗劫货车。开始大喊大叫，他们拔出枪。警方的回应是“提交在线报告”。丢失了很多个人装备，但他们没有得到乐器，所以今晚开车去萨克拉门托演奏，”视频的标题开始。</p><p>它继续说道：“他们可以拿走我们的任天堂 Switch，但他们永远无法拿走我们播放有关高速公路的摇滚歌曲的能力。严肃地说，令人震惊的是，每个人似乎都对此感到无奈。 “它发生了”。上午 9 点，在某个加油站星巴克。荒野。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DDIVv3wTzWk/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.